    "description": "Kusari Kingdom is an innovative puzzle game which uses a chain reaction mechanic similar to Dominoes falling over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748020/extras/9033320135a025b1446fec0ac5286d91.avif?t=1637367215\" width=600 height=140 /></span><br>Each level consists of an 8x8 board with enemies on it that need to be eliminated using your Defenders. <br>Defenders each have their unique pattern when triggered, activating both other Defenders and at the same time damaging enemies. With only a certain amount of triggers try to get rid of all enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748020/extras/ac5b15f33520f05e073143c1a38c9e3a.poster.avif?t=1637367215\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748020/extras/ac5b15f33520f05e073143c1a38c9e3a.webm?t=1637367215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748020/extras/ac5b15f33520f05e073143c1a38c9e3a.mp4?t=1637367215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your logic skills to defend the Kingdom against the evil forces. If a level seems too hard, you'll get hints automatically.<br><br>Multiplayer mode and more levels upcoming if there are enough voices calling for it ;)<br><br>You can try the Playtest version for free. It contains everything the full version contains except it has a reduced number of levels.",
